\c 28
\s Dhavhidhi anonyengetera kuti arwirwe naJehovha
\d Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Ndichadana kwamuri, Jehovha; Dombo rangu, regai kundinyararira; Zvimwe, kana mukandinyararira,
\s Ndingafanana navanoburukira kugomba.
\p
\v 2 Inzwai izwi remikumbiro yangu, kana ndichichema kwamuri,
\s Kana ndichisimudzira maoko angu kunzvimbo yomukati yeimba yenyu tsvene.
\p
\v 3 Musandibvuta pamwechete navakaipa,
\s Navanoita zvakashata;
\s Ivo vanotaura rugare kuna vavanogara navo,
\s Asi zvakashata zviri mumwoyo mavo.
\p
\v 4 Muvape zvakaenzana nebasa ravo, uye zvakaenzana nezvakaipa zvavakaita,
\s Muvape zvakaenzana nokubata kwamaoko avo;
\s Muvaitire sezvakavafanira.
\p
\v 5 Zvavasina kurangarira mabasa aJehovha,
\s Nezvaakabata namaoko ake,
\s Iye achavaputsa, akasavavakazve.
\p
\v 6 Jehovha ngaavongwe,
\s Nokuti akanzwa izwi rokukumbira kwangu.
\p
\v 7 Jehovha ndiye simba rangu nenhoo yangu;
\s Mwoyo wangu wakavimba naye, ndikabatsirwa;
\s Saka mwoyo wangu unofara kwazvo,
\s Ndichamurumbidza norwiyo
\s rwangu.
\p
\v 8 Jehovha ndiye simba ravo,
\s Ndiye nhare yokuponesa
\s kumuzodziwa wake.
\p
\v 9 Ponesai vanhu venyu, muropafadze nhaka yenyu;
\s Muvafudzewo, muvatakure nokusingaperi.
